.DT
move_after
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
move_after

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
move_after -  This method puts an NPC into the random movement group.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void move_after(int runaway)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^runaway%^RESET%^ - whether or not this is a wimpy attempt
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/wander_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method puts an NPC into the random movement group.
This is called from the set_move_after code in the NPC object.
You should not need to call this function directly.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
/std/npc->set_move_after()

.EP

